item.title: By: Declan Dagger
item.dc:creator: Declan Dagger
item.description:
Hi,
I'm in the process of spinning out a company from a computer science research group in TCD. We're in the personalised eLearning space and are currently looking for phase 1 co-funding. If you email me directly (Declan.DaggerATcs.tcd.ie) I can give you more details.
I look forward to hearing from you. Declan
item.content:encoded:
